  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/e916cc6e78164ed981c7c6a0b6bfee71.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=160 /></span><br><br>Hellcome is a challenging and exciting <strong>survival party game</strong> in which, players must battle their way through hordes of zombies and other hellish creatures in order to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll control various characters, each with their own unique abilities. And more playable characters and enemies are coming soon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer COOP Mode: </h2> You can team up with friends to take on the challenges of the game together. Work together to complete objectives, defeat bosses, and survive as long as possible. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense and Challenging Gameplay: </h2>Despite the lighthearted visuals, there's <strong>no auto-aim to make things easier!</strong> You'll need to rely on your own skills and reflexes to take down the zombie hordes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Abilities and Builds:</h2> Experiment with different combinations to find the ones that work best for you. With a big bunch of abilities to choose from, there's always something new to discover.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hellcome is a thrilling and challenging game that's perfect for players who love roguelite games, bullet hell shooters, and cooperative multiplayer experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/029139ff2548c27a1bfc84a8227769bd.avif?t=1726593056\" width=620 height=200 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/e916cc6e78164ed981c7c6a0b6bfee71.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=160 /></span><br><br>Hellcome is a challenging and exciting <strong>survival party game</strong> in which, players must battle their way through hordes of zombies and other hellish creatures in order to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll control various characters, each with their own unique abilities. And more playable characters and enemies are coming soon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer COOP Mode: </h2> You can team up with friends to take on the challenges of the game together. Work together to complete objectives, defeat bosses, and survive as long as possible. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.mp4